      <div class="msgContentFrame">I sat there for a couple of hours the other night letting things beat on me while I had guard up. I noticed it only skilled up if I took at least a little damage through my blocking, but for the life of me, it just won't level! Am I missing something? Is it just a bitch of a task? I'd love to get past rank 1 in shield.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><div class="msgQuote"><div class="source">Quote:</div><div class="orig">An owl and a squirrel are sitting in a tree, watching a farmer go by. The owl turns to the squirrel and says nothing, because owls can't talk. <br /> <br />The owl then eats the squirrel because it's a bird of prey.</div></div></div></div>
