      <div class="msgContentFrame">I think they can make Sentinal more fun if they increase the time Guard lasts, or at the very least have the time increase as you rank up in skill.  The second route seems more logical since as you get better at something it would only make sense that you can hold your guard. <br /> <br />All in all Sentinal with Phalanx is pretty awesome and you can do loads of damage and have a ton of TP for other weapon skills/abilities.  <br /> <br /></div>
